column1: Morning Sun Martial Arts & Education Center

Merced Mixed Martial Arts Academy in Merced, California, is owned by Tom Theofanopoulos, who also owns and operates Oakdale Mixed Martial Arts Academy since 1988. Tom has over 30 years experience in the Martial Arts, including titles in Wrestling (Junior Olympic Competitor), Traditional Karate (8th Degree Black belt), Kajukenbo (Professor title), Jiu Jitsu (Black Belt) under the Behring Family System and four-time US Open Champion.

Downham’s Kenpo Karate is dedicated to the ideal that there should be no bullies.  We teach our students to be discerning about when to and when not to use their physical skills.  Part of what they learn is how to be confident in the face of bullying.

International Self Defense Institute is a martial arts studio with years of experience in Shaolin Kempo combined with Shotokan karate. Very knowledgeable and experienced instructors teach all of our classes and place a strong emphasis on teaching discipline, building energy, increasing self-confidence and improving concentration. Our courses are perfect for children, teenagers and adults. They will also help you develop self-defense skills, physical conditioning, and self-discipline.

The Academy of Tae Kwon Do, located at 988 Oak Street in San Francisco, was established in 1979 by Professor Bill Dewart. It is associated with S. Henry Cho's Karate Institute in New York City, one of the oldest Martial Arts schools in the United States. The classes at the academy are open to everyone. Please call or stop by for more information about classes offered or special arrangements.  Tae Kwon Do is a philosophy. It utilizes the practice of a martial art as a mean of achieving both mental and physical harmony. The Academy seeks to develop the "whole" the student, both the mind and the body.

James Reed's Tae Kwon Do is in the business of providing the best martial arts training at the most affordable rate for all students and families.  We emphasize discipline, self respect and honor.  We have been in business for nine years in Tracy and plan to be here for many years to come

At Five Claw Martial Arts, we teach a wide range of students of all ages and abilities. We individualize the instruction for each student to meet his or her unique goal—whether it be to learn a self-defense art, increase physical fitness, or train as an MMA fighter.

column1: International Budo Academy of The Martial Arts
column8: The International Budo Academy of the Martial Arts is a family dojo specializing in the arts of traditional Okinawan Karate and Kobudo.

column1: Sun Yi's Academy of Tae Kwon Do
column8: Here at Sun Yi’s Academy in Arcata we believe in a holistic and balanced approach to training, as well as life. We strive to offer our members opportunities to foster a Sound Mind, and Sound Body by providing a diverse array of classes and services, and a high quality of instruction and facilities.

Our philosophy promotes respect and discipline while learning a traditional art form with self-defense skills in a safe and fun environment. Your child will learn the following skills in our classroom such as respect, focus, coordination, discipline, concentration, and confidence, while learning self-defense skills in our safe, fun and positive environment. Many of our young students have achieved awards in competitions locally, nationally, and internationally. Many students have also been able to have the experience of performing for local events and televised productions.

Aikido (eye-key-dough) is a unique Japanese martial art renown for its graceful power, ethical ideals, and brilliant conflict resolution strategies. Aikido blends the best aspects of ancient martial arts with a modern teaching style and social structure. Full Circle Aikido is non-competitive, challenging, and fun.

Karate is an outstanding way for kids and adults to improve physically and mentally. As students advance from white through black belt, they gain advantages of strength, flexibility and endurance, as well as improved concentration, discipline and character. The All American Black Belt Academy, located in Dublin, California, is family oriented and offers instruction in the Shito Ryu style of Japanese karate. The All American Black Belt Academy has several locations in Northern California.

The name "Trad Am Karate" or the initials "TAK" are used as abbreviations for our system and style, Traditional American Karate. The school names TRAD AM KARATE (Santee) and ALPINE KARATE ACADEMY (Alpine) personalize these schools as there are other TAK schools owned and operated by officially authorized TAK instructors. Traditional American Karate provides a good system of martial arts suitable for the American way of life and philosophy. TAK emphasizes the development of attitude as well as knowledge and skill. In TAK, the objective is not to teach a certain defense for a certain attack, but rather to help students develop 'intuition' in which they are free from preconceived actions. To achieve this, Traditional American Karate is organized into formal kata, situational self-defense techniques, sparring techniques, and many hand, foot and body change techniques. We also include Oriental weaponry.

column1: Kicks Tae Kwon Do, Kick Boxing & MMA

Children’s aikido classes expose kids to a mixture of formal techniques, movement skills and games designed to foster an understanding of aikido’s basic principles. Colored belts are awarded at the discretion of the instructor for progress made while training. The testing process is designed to enhance confidence and self-esteem.

Jobu Shin Kan is a traditional martial arts school dedicated to development of character through the study of Danzan Ryu Jujitsu. We welcome students of all ages, sizes, and body types.

27 Years serving families in Martial Arts Instruction and Leadership Development. Our instruction is acclaimed “One of the finest in the world.”Tiny Tigers beginning at age 3 and 4, Little Dragons ages 5 & 6, Dragons ages 7 to 11, Traditional ages 12 to 29 and Songin minimum age 30.

Shou Shu is the ultimate art of unarmed combat as well as being a superb system in achieving physical fitness and confidence in oneself. This is an unsurpassed system of self-defense which combines a vast array of pressure points and joint locking techniques (Chin Na) with kicking, punching, throwing, falling, (Shuai-Chiao) and a myriad of fighting techniques (San Sao’s) into beautiful and dynamic ‘soft-style’ emphasizing speed, fluidity and power.
To touch many peoples lives with self-defense training while promoting safety, health, confidence, discicpline and respect

While the physical movements of martial arts will teach your children self defense and enhance their coordination, you will also see growth in their focus, concentration and respect for others. Martial arts will give your child a strong sense of confidence and develop the discipline to never misuse their skills. While learning and developing in each of these important areas, your child will be in a positive environment, setting and meeting goals, and having lots of fun achieving them!
mixed martial arts, self defense karate, children and adult classes, private lessons, birthday parties, martial art weapon training

We offer a family-oriented, friendly environment, dedicated to the ageless martial arts disciplines of self control, physical fitness, and self-defense. Our karate classes will condition your body and give you new skills, plus teach you how defend yourself and your family from a real-life violent assault. And that knowledge will be yours for life!

column1: Golden Drago Jeet Kune Do Academy
column8: GDJKD is based on Science and Psychology. With over 40 years of research and development. At the Golden Dragon Jeet Kune Do Academy, you will find no gimmicks or useless fancy moves. Our philosophy is simple: keeping it as real as possible and providing mental and physical strategies on how to survive any attack.

MMA is not just for the macho guys, we welcome all shapes, sizes and most ages. Whether your goal is to get in shape, lose weight, defend yourself, fight off stress or try something new we’ve got a class for you. It doesn’t matter if the most experience you’ve had is wrestling your little brother when you were a kid, or you are looking to expand your study of martial arts, we have the equipment and instructing skills you need to accommodate what you need to grow and learn.

Tournament House Sports & Fitness Center is committed to the health and fitness of our members and community.  We offer an exciting variety of fitness and cardio classes, a senior fitness program, martial arts, fencing, self-defense classes, weight rooms, resistance equipment, and more.  Tournament House boasts the finest personal training staff in the Inland Empire and we emphasize a well balanced life style complemented by health and fitness basics that can be maintained for a lifetime.  Tournament House has over 20,000 square feet of state of the art cardio and fitness equipment, racquetball, handball, basketball, locker rooms with whirlpool spas, tanning, and saunas.  We offer child care on the premises.

Acupuncture Plus offers a complete system of Oriental Medicine and acupuncture for all diseases and imbalances. Chinese medicine is a complete medical system that has diagnosed, treated, and prevented illness for over 23 centuries. While it can remedy ailments and alter states of mind, Chinese medicine can also enhance recuperative power, immunity, and the capacity for pleasure, work and creativity.

Ito's White Tiger Dojo has been offering classes and private instruction in the martial arts since 1979. Ito's White Tiger Dojo is a family owned martial arts studio focused on the discipline of the mind, body and spirit. Special introduction and family rates are available. Ken Nagayama Martial Arts is a combination of several Martial Arts styles. The foundation of this system is an Okinawan form of Karate called Moto Bu Ryu. Originally taught only to the royal family of Okinawa, Moto Bu Ryu was the highest form of Martial Art developed to help the royal family remain just that; royal.

Our teaching is done as if we were working with our own family.

column1: United Self Defense Academy Hayastan MMA
column8: Our youth programs are not just another after-school activity.  Soccer, baseball, football, basketball are all great activities for children, but our programs are about personal development through a physical discipline.  Martial Arts is not a team sport.  The only person that you are competing with is “yourself.”  Some students are in shape, while others are overweight.  Some come for self defense or fitness, and others for fun.  Each person is treated as an equal, and is trained to the best of their own ability and potential.

Even though self-defense is the theme of the instruction, there is also other attributes that are focused upon in the training such as: Self-Control, Coordination,     Balance, Agility, as well as Concentration, Focus and Awareness. These skills are not just for self-defense, but for other endeavors in life, school, sports, jobs etc.

column1: Santa Clarita Valley School of Jujitsu
column8: Danzan Ryu Jujitsu training involves learning to roll and fall (Sutemi), to move and balance (Tai Sabaki), to escape from grabs and manipulate joints (Yawara), to throw & project (Nage), to submit an opponent (Shime), to counter and transition (Oku), to access and express your inner being (Shinnin), as well as many other in-depth areas of focus.

Delta Martial Arts and Athletics is a facility for martial arts and athletic training, we want to create through education and training a place where people can be inspired to change and improve through the physical activities they participate in.

column1: Way of The Bear & Tiger Karate

column8: GymStars and Tibon-Goju Ryu deliver the best in martial arts training.  We have developed National, International, Pan-American, and World Class athletes who have represented the United States all over the world.  GOJU means hard soft style of Karate.  We use the hard style of Okinawan/Japanese straight line linear angles in fighting and the soft style angels of redirection and the yielding of Chinese Kempo.  We offer classes for ages of 3 to 16.  We teach beginners to black belt including weapons training of the Yamani Ryu Okinawa Kobudo System.  "Our commitment is to develop excellence in self-confidence, respect and discipline in all students so they develop into the best they can be." Sensei Tibon.

A favorite slogan here at Trad Am is, "the family that punches and kicks together, sticks together."

Through the martial arts our students become more confident and develop an attitude of self-reliance. column1: Happy Ocean Tai Chi Kung Fu Acacdemy

His system of teaching is unique because he shows his students how Tai Chi builds on 12 circular movements and 13 components. It is based on what he has found to be most effective over the years that he has been studying, practicing and teaching Tai Chi. Chi Kung exercises round out the system for maximum health benefits. The Happy Ocean Tai Chi program encompasses breathing techniques, balance, understanding Yin Yan, forms for practice, equipment for strengthening and improving skills, and using everyday, common objects as weapons for self defense. Learning this Tai Chi and Chi Kung program will harmonize your Mind, Body, and Spirit.

Martial Arts training at USSD is not just about physical fitness or self-defense. Our students develop a range of skills that enable them to succeed in all areas of life. This is particularly important for children, who need the guidance and support of parents and others to develop the skills they need to become capable and balanced adults. Along with improved coordination, flexibility, strength, and endurance, our students develop better concentration skills, a sense of calmness, and a deep respect for themselves and others, in an environment where the camaraderie created by shared challenges creates a sense of trust and a recognition of individual achievement. Students advance at their own pace, without the pressure that is often such a part of team sports.

column1: Kung Fu San Soo Diamond Bar
column8: Kung Fu San Soo is considered, by many, to be the most sophisticated and complete form of martial art in existence today. In the December 1999 issue of Inside Kung Fu Magazine San Soo is referred to as “Legendary and Devastating… A pure Chinese fighting art that has few equals.” These statements could be considered opinion and many consider them fact, but all agree, Kung Fu San Soo is not a sport. By its very definition, the complete use of a man in the art of hand-to-hand combat, San Soo cannot conform to the specifications of being a sport. Sports are governed by a set of rules. However, if a set of rules were applied to San Soo, a fighter’s techniques would be limited and they would no longer be utilizing the principles of Kung Fu San Soo.

We offer a variety of programs that will fit the needs of everyone. If you are interested in MMA, karate, Brazilian jiu-jitsu, kickboxing, or just want to get fit, then we have something for you! We are dedicated to providing a fun, safe, and family-oriented martial arts experience for students of all ages. Our mission is to make our students more successful in life through martial arts and fitness.

Il-Do Taekwondo highlights the best of martial arts as a way of life, not just a form of self defense. Our philosophy is rooted in basic, fundamental human behavior. We teach Taekwondo as a way of establishing the true meaning of our tenets: courtesy, integrity, perserverance, self-control and an indomitable spirit. Il-Do Taekwondo continues to produce countless black belts that have learned more than just a means of taking care of themselves physically but mentally as well. This unity of mind and body is what it takes to be stronger, better people and the results are students with the ability to lead and set an example for others to follow
Kata in it's simplest form is a series of defensive and offensive techniques that were put together in a specific combination that can be interpreted in many ways.
Hwa Rang Do Academy is dedicated to promoting health, strength and longevity.

Soo Bahk Do® is a Korean traditional martial art whose history dates back many centuries. Kicking techniques, for which Soo Bahk Do® is renowned, are based on the Moo Duk Kwan® style as developed by Grandmaster Hwang Kee.

column8: Guangxi Martial Arts – Tyrrell Academy is where children, youth/teens, and adults can learn contemporary and traditional Martial Arts. Gracie Barra Carlsbad maintains the proud legacy of Gracie Barra, which has produced some of the world’s most dominant Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu champions. But Gracie Barra Carlsbad isn’t just about producing tournament champions. In fact, we believe the greatest victories are those won in life, off the mats and away from any crowd.

At Brigada Elite we work on developing our members striking skills, while try to help them get in shape to live a healthier life. Our kids program is for Muay Thai and Boxing, which helps provide discipline, confidence, and physical fitness.

Our teen program is simple and effective , you can take advantage of all classes five days a week . At Reign Training Center, we offer some amazing programs in the disciplines of wrestling, jiu-jitsu, kickboxing, boxing, and strength/conditioning. We are the home to the first official USA Wrestling Regional Training Center in South Orange County, which is led by head coaches Mark Muñoz (NCAA Div I National Champion/CA Hall of Fame Member) and Valentin Kalika (California National Coach). At AB MMA Academy, you will learn and gain important skills to improve your fighting techniques as well as your daily life. Learn how to defend yourself and master true discipline through any one of our classes!

One Martial Arts features award-winning programs for people of all ages that are focused on character development and life-skills education. Our caring instructional staff believes in traditional martial arts values such as respect, discipline and commitment.  We balance our teachings with progressive and innovative methods to help you succeed in life.

column8: Our unique programs are designed to get your children in a positive emotional state and keep them there. Your child will be athletically fit which will give him /her confidence to achieve more in life. We have carefully designed our program to gradually teach our students how to deal with fear, worry, doubt, boredom and lack of a goal. These are the five things that prevent people from achieving a peaceful life. The students will learn to choose to remain positive under any condition and keep a healthy attitude about the circumstances surrounding them. With time they will eliminate fear, worry, doubt, boredom and they will find a meaningful goal with a good intention behind it, pursue it with passion and gain more trust and confidence in themselves.

We offer the best Kids’ Program here at Faction! Our Kids’ Jiu-Jitsu and Kickboxing classes will increase your child’s self-confidence, discipline, self control, and fitness level. Through drills, techniques, and games, your children will master these martial arts and most importantly, learn self defense in a fun encouraging environment.

We are a family-oriented martial art based on Korean traditions. Our mission is to develop mental and physical strength and well-being through the practice of martial arts. Practice of Kuk Sool Won is a great way to get in shape and learn self-defense in an environment where mutual respect and courtesy are a high priority... It's fun too!

Welcome to Undisputed El Cajon, located in the heart of El Cajon’s downtown district. We are a full range fitness facility established in 2007 specializing in boxing, mixed martial arts, muay thai, jiu jitsu and strength and conditioning.

Now more than ever we want our children to grow up independent, healthy, physically fit, and with high self esteem. Our Kids Boxing Program provides just that unique formula found lacking in many other youth activities out there.

Woodall’s Self-Defense has a program that is developed especially for children ages 7 and up. Our programs are not only fun and interesting, but they have a foundation in teaching theory that is used by elementary school teachers and other professionals working in early childhood education.

At Red Dragon Karate, children will learn the art of self-defense through the extensive training of various forms of martial arts. Our fun children programs teaches children the necessary qualities of respect and self-discipline, in addition to focusing on skills and character development. This helps them excel in other aspects of life as well and lays a strong foundation for their future.

The trainers and staff at Xfit & Combat Sports are courteous professionals. We have some of the most experienced trainers available. No matter what type of training you are interested in from starting a path to the UFC or getting into the best shape of your life, our staff at Xfit & Combat Sports will be dedicated to helping you achieve your goals!!

Gracie Gym is part of the largest and most traditional Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu Family Organization in the World. Our schools, Instructors, and Competitors are present not only in the United States or Brazil, but all over the world. Gracie Gym offers its members a new kind of workout environment based on the Gracie Family’s 88-year commitment to Martial Arts, Fitness, Health, and Wellbeing.

Our Kids Program is designed to teach boys and girls, ages 4-15, the basics and fundamentals of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. We are dedicated to improving the quality of the students' lives through the practice of Martial Arts.

Fitness Fanatics promotes non-violence in the instruction of our technique. In our civilized society, education now fosters the power of the mind, articulating yourself out of confrontation, using your head not just your heart and being diplomatic. No one wins a war--be smart. The martial artist has practiced the art of self-defense and the need for controlling the situation. As Sun Tzu proclaims, "The true object of war is peace."

Come in for a different approach to mixed martial arts training. Be efficient in all ranges of combat: kicking, boxing, trapping, grappling, ground and weaponry. Let us introduce you to Jeet Kune Do; the art and philosophy of the late Bruce Lee. Head instructor Sifu/Guro Bud Thompson met Bruce Lee and Dan Inosanto in 1965 and has been practicing and passing on this legendary art ever since. He is an authentic second generation Jun Fan Gung Fu/Jeet Kune Do instructor.

There are many reasons that kids and adults alike are drawn to train in Kenpo Karate. Some are drawn to the physical fitness and weight-loss aspects of training. Others seek to add discipline and self control to their lives. While still others are concerned about safety and self-defense. Also students unexpectly find themselves on the path of self discovery. Martial arts training over time can teach you many things about yourself and the world around you.

Our goal as an academy is to help you achieve your goals as a Martial Artist: whether that be to learn how to defend yourself, get an introduction to Mixed Martial Arts (MMA), improve your physical fitness, lose weight, or to simply have a fun hobby. Our classes are catered to men, women, teenagers, and kids.

With the goal to instill confidence in children to overcome bullying without violence, your child will gain the self-confidence, physical tools, and emotional maturity they need to avoid or resolve confrontation in a constructive manner. These classes are open to children of all ages as bullying never really goes away - it just becomes more subtle and covert. Young adults need to be able to cope with it as well.

Our programs cater to different abilities and learning styles, which means you’ll always receive the specific attention you need to reach your goals safely and effectively.
